

This is the runtime library for the VnV injection point system

To Install, there are three steps. 

1. Install ADIOS2 and export ADIOS2_DIR=<install-path>


2. Install XPLUS2XSD and export XPLUS2XSD_DIR=<install-path>
   cd xplus-xsd
   export XPLUS2XSD_DIR=<install-location>
   ./autogen.sh
   ./configure --prefix=${XPLUS2XSD_DIR} 
   make
   (sudo) make install   

3. Generate the vv_schema api. 
   cd injection

   # Set the XSD install directory then

   make-generate-api 

4. Build the injection library
   cd injection
   make 

5. cd examples/dummy
   make
   cd executables
   ./sample.a



